-- GIT & Github Difference --

Git => main codebase software 
Github => Same as git but in website 

-- Features ---

Git => 
Branch 
Push Request / Pull Request
Fork 

cd ( change directory )

Working Area = Normal Folder & Files not cared by GIT
Tracked Area = Normal Folder & Files known by GIT
Staging Area = Folder and Files GIT will upload
Git Directory = Folder and Files GIT uploaded by GIT

